    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather still carries its factory scent, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is superlative, backed by a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists. It has never seen inclement weather, has zero underbody corrosion, and has been driven sparingly by a dedicated enthusiast. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example that satisfies the most rigorous standards of excellence.",
